[Queen of Darkness]

9
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:54,000
[Episode 21]

10
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:13,616
Ti Cha.

11
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:14,640
What are you doing?

12
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:18,040
I know it was wrong of me
to expose mother-in-law's crimes.

13
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:20,576
But we can still talk this through calmly.

14
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:22,440
Haven't I treated you well enough?

15
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:25,280
Why are you doing this to my mom?

16
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:27,040
Do you know?

17
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:29,880
Mom wanted me to divorce you

18
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,840
just to get the shares in my hand.

19
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,640
Is this really

20
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:34,256
thinking of you?

21
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,280
No way.

22
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:37,576
I already talked to my mom.

23
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,160
She'll treat you better from now on.

24
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:41,720
We could've had a happy life together.

25
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,920
But it's you.

26
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:47,160
You ruined everything!

27
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,800
Haven't you seen

28
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,240
how mom treated me these days?

29
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:56,040
Do you really think
she'll let us live in peace?

30
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,640
Calm down and think carefully.

31
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,280
If your mom weren't around,

32
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:07,320
wouldn't our lives be so much happier?

33
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:10,416
Let go of me first.

34
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,776
Just let go of me.

35
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,440
We can talk this out calmly.

36
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:18,920
Stop trying to fool me.

37
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,936
You think I don't know?

38
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,520
You're taking revenge on us.

39
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,176
Once you get your revenge,

40
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,440
you'll leave me.

41
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,360
Well, now,

42
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,000
you can't go anywhere.

43
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,976
You can stay by my side for life.

44
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,857
Relax.

45
00:02:40,881 --> 00:02:44,400
I'll turn this room into a grand palace.

46
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,240
So that for the rest of your life,

47
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,000
you'll live in total luxury.

48
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:12,920
Ti Cha.

49
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,240
Relax.

50
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:16,080
Look what's on your waist.

51
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,960
Don't move.

52
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,480
Otherwise,

53
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,560
if I accidentally press the remote,

54
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,536
this bomb

55
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,120
will go off ahead of time.

56
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:36,960
What do you want?

57
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,696
[Separation Agreement]
Sign the Separation Agreement.

58
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,000
Then I'll let you live.

59
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,240
No way.

60
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,960
Even if I die,

61
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,120
you'll still be Ti Cha's widow.

62
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,256
You can never

63
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,536
get rid of

64
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:58,160
the title of being my wife!

65
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,960
So stubborn.

66
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,297
I just wonder if your fate

67
00:04:03,321 --> 00:04:04,560
is as tough as your mouth.

68
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,296
You wicked woman.

69
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,400
Wicked woman!

70
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:34,977
At this close range,

71
00:04:35,001 --> 00:04:36,160
you'll be blown up too!

72
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,497
Stop it!

73
00:04:38,521 --> 00:04:39,560
Stop right now!

74
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,896
Are you out of your mind?

75
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,920
Lost your mind?

76
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,280
I'll sign! I'll sign!

77
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,600
Wicked woman!

78
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:25,880
A servant can quit anytime,

79
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,400
but because of a marriage certificate,

80
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,760
I have to live as your prisoner forever.

81
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,656
And still take your blows.

82
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,800
Getting yelled at by you.

83
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:36,080
Then humiliated and tormented by you.

84
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,720
And I still have to watch you
fool around with someone else.

85
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:41,376
Who do you think you are?
(Watch on www.kisskh.ca to support Admin)

86
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:42,800
You enjoy hitting people, right?

87
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,776
You like putting women down, right?

88
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,640
You like watching others suffer,
don't you?

89
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,560
Weren't you supposed to be all tough?

90
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:51,960
What's wrong now?

91
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,656
Getting scared?

92
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,960
Just because of a bomb,

93
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:57,160
and you're already trembling
like a mouse?

94
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,640
Actually, I know.

95
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,520
I know

96
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,520
you're not An Ning.

97
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,840
And it's exactly because
you're not An Ning

98
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,320
that I've fallen for you.

99
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,760
My father's dominance.

100
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,400
My mother's twisted need for control.

101
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,160
They turned me into who I am today.

102
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,560
The reason I don't want a divorce

103
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:29,840
is that I know

104
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,720
after the divorce

105
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,800
I'll never see you again.

106
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,056
To you, women

107
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,816
are just tools for sexual release

108
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,040
and trophies to show off.

109
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,960
Have you ever truly respected a woman?

110
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:55,560
Do you even understand
what makes a woman so precious?

111
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:58,320
Have you ever given her
even an ounce of genuine care?

112
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:00,200
Someone like you

113
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,920
isn't worthy of saying the word "love".

114
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:14,400
Ye Ying!

115
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,920
Ye Ying!

116
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,600
Ye Ying!

117
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:51,696
That vile woman ruined my family.

118
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:54,320
Today, I'll send you to hell
with my own hands.

119
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,680
Go to hell, you sneaky woman!

120
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,696
The forecast said it would rain today,

121
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,920
but the rain hasn't come yet.

122
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,600
I didn't expect I'd use it on you first.

123
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,280
I'll fight you!

124
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:19,320
That's what they call
paying for your own mistake.

125
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:33,856
Dad.

126
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:35,640
Even if I wipe out every enemy I have,

127
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:39,120
I'll never hear you call me Ying again.

128
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:52,457
Where's Rong?

129
00:08:52,481 --> 00:08:53,616
Miss.

130
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,216
Rong hasn't come back yet.

131
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,400
His phone's unreachable too.

132
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,737
Miss.

133
00:09:05,761 --> 00:09:07,640
We searched every place

134
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:10,360
and found signs of a fight
at Rong's place.

135
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:11,920
They left this behind.

136
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,576
If you want to save Rong,

137
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,456
the Ye family's daughter
must come in person.

138
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,960
Deadline is 12 o'clock tonight.

139
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:22,936
It's Song Pa.

140
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:25,040
Why does he want you to go?

141
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,760
He must have guessed my identity.

142
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,936
So he used Rong as bait

143
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,040
and set up this trap

144
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:33,000
to lure me in
and expose me face to face.

145
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,656
Once they confirm I'm Ye Ying,

146
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:36,056
it proves An Ning is dead.

147
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,176
Then they can take over
An Ning's shares.

148
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:37,897
Miss.

149
00:09:37,921 --> 00:09:39,296
You mustn't go there.

150
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,800
He won't let you off that easily.

151
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,400
If my father were still alive,

152
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,760
he'd never let his brothers die for him.

153
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:48,160
Besides,

154
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,216
Song Pa

155
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,296
will only get more ruthless

156
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,440
if his plan fails.

157
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:53,936
You think I'd let the Qingyun Gang

158
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,200
be bullied by him like that?

159
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,296
[Operating Room/Ward]

160
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:59,320
[Patient: Huo Xiao]

161
